title: Rando[m] ConverZations: Sam and Joey talk about the Jordan Peterson Meetup in Chicago
description:
Sam and Joey talk a little about their pasts and about starting a meetup in the Chicagoland area.

Here are the event details for the very first JBP Chicagoland meetup...

Date: Wed November 6th, 2019
Time: 7:00 pm through 9:00 pm

Place: 
Wheaton Christian Reformed Church 
711 E Harrison Ave 
Wheaton, IL 60187

Additional Info:
The are two buildings, the sanctuary and a smaller structure. The meeting is located at the smaller structure.

Find meaningful conversations on the Bridges of Meaning Discord:
https://discord.gg/zdjzsFu
